value.title: Video shows Romney being called "traitor" by Trump fans while on flight
value.excerpt: Senator Mitt Romney of Utah faced chants of "traitor" while on a flight from Salt Lake City to Washington, D.C. A video posted to Twitter appears to show a small group of passengers chanting, at least one of whom appears to not be properly wearing a mask.

value.title: Trump signs order banning transactions with Chinese apps Alipay and WeChat Pay
value.excerpt: Taking his campaign against Chinese technology down to the wire, President Trump on Tuesday signed an executive order banning transactions with a number of Chinese mobile apps, including Alipay and WeChat Pay.

value.title: Trump Signs Order Banning Alipay and Other Chinese Apps
value.excerpt: WASHINGTON—President Trump signed an executive order banning transactions with Chinese payment platform Alipay and other Chinese apps. Write to Andrew Restuccia at Andrew.Restuccia@wsj.com and John D. McKinnon at john.mckinnon@wsj.com

value.title: Joe Biden was ‘legitimately’ elected, majority of Georgia voters say
value.excerpt: Joe Biden "legitimately" defeated President Trump in November's election, 61 percent of Georgia voters say, according to preliminary data from the Fox News Voter Analysis, a survey of more than 4,000 voters in the state.

value.title: 'Trump is my president': Protesters gather in DC a day before Congress certifies election
value.excerpt: Crowds gathered in Washington on Tuesday, a day before larger rallies and a congressional vote to certify the election are planned.

value.title: Biden to focus on Covid relief for small businesses in Wednesday speech
